full_text:

full_text: @pangopup I just tried to look up the book I found, but can't seem to find it and can't remember the name, but after like 90 minutes of frantic searching  I found this fantastic hardcover book on apes with stunning huge full-page high res photos, and the gorilla looked sweet.
full_text(utf-8): b"@pangopup I just tried to look up the book I found, but can't seem to find it and can't remember the name, but after like 90 minutes of frantic searching  I found this fantastic hardcover book on apes with stunning huge full-page high res photos, and the gorilla looked sweet."

full_text: @pangopup Turns out Google images only has really shitty pictures of gorillas, or decent pictures but at really low resolution, which will not do. So set out early o'clock to get into Norwich and go to literally every bookshop I'm aware of to find good gorilla pics.
full_text(utf-8): b"@pangopup Turns out Google images only has really shitty pictures of gorillas, or decent pictures but at really low resolution, which will not do. So set out early o'clock to get into Norwich and go to literally every bookshop I'm aware of to find good gorilla pics."

full_text: @pangopup So I have until midday the next day to decide what I'm getting and find a source picture for him to work from. First idea was a Bill Hicks portrait but I eventually decide against that and go for a character from one of my favourite books, a telepathic gorilla called Ishmael.
full_text(utf-8): b"@pangopup So I have until midday the next day to decide what I'm getting and find a source picture for him to work from. First idea was a Bill Hicks portrait but I eventually decide against that and go for a character from one of my favourite books, a telepathic gorilla called Ishmael."

full_text: @pangopup He explains he'll be tattooing me the next day with a realism/B&G piece of my choice. I immediately asked to see his portfolio in case I have to nope my way out of there, but fortunately it turned out he was really really good and I liked his style.
full_text(utf-8): b"@pangopup He explains he'll be tattooing me the next day with a realism/B&G piece of my choice. I immediately asked to see his portfolio in case I have to nope my way out of there, but fortunately it turned out he was really really good and I liked his style."

full_text: @pangopup End of day, after not winning best large black-and-grey tattoo (I was robbed), they pull the raffle winners. One of my numbers gets called and I nervously wander up and tell them it's me. Get called up on stage, introduced to a tattoo artist, and we shake hands for a photo.
full_text(utf-8): b"@pangopup End of day, after not winning best large black-and-grey tattoo (I was robbed), they pull the raffle winners. One of my numbers gets called and I nervously wander up and tell them it's me. Get called up on stage, introduced to a tattoo artist, and we shake hands for a photo."
